            We guarantee a response within 24 hours on business days (Monday-Friday). For urgent enquiries, WhatsApp us directly for the fastest response.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-zinc-50 rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 p-6 hover:border-[#a78656] transition-colors">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none font-semibold text-zinc-900">
            <span>Do you work with couples outside Italy?</span>
